</div>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369192" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone23.png" alt="" width="1076" height="1438" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone23.png 1076w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone23-360x481.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone23-768x1026.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone23-766x1024.png 766w" sizes="(max-width: 1076px) 100vw, 1076px" /></h3>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ iPhone 11 夜景模式拍摄，自然的夜间观感</p>
</div>
<h3><strong>国内厂商奋起直追</strong></h3>
<p>iPhone 在提升，国产安卓厂商也没原地不动。</p>
<p>以华为代表的国内手机厂商，在设计摄影方面取得了重大突破。</p>
<p><strong>1. 更高的像素</strong></p>
<p>以小米 10 Ultra 为例，主摄像头的像素高达 4800 万，<strong>是 iPhone 11 摄像头像素 4 倍</strong>。虽说像素不是成片质量的唯一决定，但更高的像素确实在部分场景下有不小的优势，拍得更清晰。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369242" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone27.jpg" alt="" width="2992" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone27.jpg 2992w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone27-360x481.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone27-768x1027.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone27-766x1024.jpg 766w" sizes="(max-width: 2992px) 100vw, 2992px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 小米 10 Ultra 拍摄. 图片来自：DXOMARK</p>
</div>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369243" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone29.jpg" alt="" width="4000" height="3000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone29.jpg 4000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone29-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone29-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone29-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 4000px) 100vw, 4000px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 小米 10 Ultra 拍摄. 图片来自：DXOMARK</p>
</div>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369245" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Bokeh_13-5_XiaomiMi10Ultra.jpg" alt="" width="2992" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Bokeh_13-5_XiaomiMi10Ultra.jpg 2992w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Bokeh_13-5_XiaomiMi10Ultra-360x481.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Bokeh_13-5_XiaomiMi10Ultra-768x1027.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Bokeh_13-5_XiaomiMi10Ultra-766x1024.jpg 766w" sizes="(max-width: 2992px) 100vw, 2992px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 小米 10 Ultra 拍摄. 图片来自：DXOMARK</p>
</div>
<p><strong>2. 更大尺寸的 CMOS 传感器</strong></p>
<p>同等像素下，传感器越大，单一像素的面积也相应越大，其接受光信号的能力越强，捕获的光子越多，于是信噪比提高，得到的画质越出色。</p>
<p>例如<strong>华为 P40 Pro， CMOS 尺寸为 1/1.28 英寸</strong>，比不少卡片相机的传感器尺寸还要大，其摄影「超感光」的底气正是来自这里，「底大一级压死人」的营销深入人心。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369247" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/TrapezeNeighborhood_HuaweiP40Pro_05-00.jpg" alt="" width="4096" height="3072" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/TrapezeNeighborhood_HuaweiP40Pro_05-00.jpg 4096w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/TrapezeNeighborhood_HuaweiP40Pro_05-00-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/TrapezeNeighborhood_HuaweiP40Pro_05-00-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/TrapezeNeighborhood_HuaweiP40Pro_05-00-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 4096px) 100vw, 4096px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ P40 Pro 拍摄. 图片来自：DXOMARK</p>
</div>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369248" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/LaRegie_HuaweiP40Pro_05-00.jpg" alt="" width="3072" height="4096" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/LaRegie_HuaweiP40Pro_05-00.jpg 3072w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/LaRegie_HuaweiP40Pro_05-00-360x480.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/LaRegie_HuaweiP40Pro_05-00-768x1024.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 3072px) 100vw, 3072px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ P40 Pro 拍摄. 图片来自：DXOMARK</p>
</div>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369249" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/FlashOffBridge_HuaweiP40Pro_05-00.jpg" alt="" width="4096" height="3072" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/FlashOffBridge_HuaweiP40Pro_05-00.jpg 4096w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/FlashOffBridge_HuaweiP40Pro_05-00-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/FlashOffBridge_HuaweiP40Pro_05-00-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/FlashOffBridge_HuaweiP40Pro_05-00-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 4096px) 100vw, 4096px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ P40 Pro 拍摄. 图片来自：DXOMARK</p>
</div>
<p><strong>3. 更多倍数的变焦</strong></p>
<p>如今十倍变焦算是旗舰机的门槛，<strong>百倍变焦</strong>也不稀奇。</p>
<p>三星、华为、小米、OPPO、vivo 等厂商推出了自己的多倍变焦机型，一个比一个拍得远，给用户呈现更加丰富的照片细节。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369260" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/sanxing.png" alt="" width="2156" height="1208" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/sanxing.png 2156w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/sanxing-360x202.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/sanxing-768x430.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/sanxing-1024x574.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2156px) 100vw, 2156px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 三星 S20 Ultra 官网展示的多倍变焦图片</p>
</div>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369261" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/sanxing2.png" alt="" width="2154" height="1208" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/sanxing2.png 2154w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/sanxing2-360x202.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/sanxing2-768x431.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/sanxing2-1024x574.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2154px) 100vw, 2154px" /></p>
