<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 三星 S20 Ultra 拍摄. 图片来自：DXOMARK</p>
</div>
<h3><strong>iPhone 也有力不从心时</strong></h3>
<p>从 4 开始使用 iPhone 这么多年，我想说一句可能让部分人不太舒服的话：<strong>在某些方面，iPhone 拍照是掉队了</strong>。</p>
<p>这个「掉队」的意思，并不是因为 iPhone 自己退步了，iPhone 的进步有目共睹，「掉队」的原因是竞争对手进步的幅度更大。</p>
<p>以 DXOMARK 为例，iPhone 11 Pro 的摄影排名目前位于第十多位，从这家摄影评测机构公布的照片看，iPhone 11 Pro 在某些维度上似乎还不如价格仅一半的国产竞品。（当然也有人质疑 DXOMARK 的测评规则，认为其「收大钱恰烂饭」，这个不在本文的讨论范围内。）</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369278" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_1857.jpeg" alt="" width="4032" height="6048" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_1857.jpeg 4032w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_1857-360x540.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_1857-768x1152.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_1857-683x1024.jpeg 683w" sizes="(max-width: 4032px) 100vw, 4032px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 上图 iPhone 11 Pro 拍摄，下图 P40 Pro 拍摄，iPhone 拍的照片在清晰度、色彩表现和景深控制方面略逊一筹. 图片来自： DXOMARK</p>
</div>
<p>从我个人使用体验来看，<strong>iPhone 有不少地方暂时无法满足我的需求</strong>。</p>
<p>例如，我希望超广角镜头的像素高一点，拍出来的照片清晰一点，但 iPhone 11 系列的超广角成片远不如主摄清晰。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369199" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone25.png" alt="" width="1342" height="1796" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone25.png 1342w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone25-360x482.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone25-768x1028.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone25-765x1024.png 765w" sizes="(max-width: 1342px) 100vw, 1342px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 光线不足时，超广角摄像头画质明显下降</p>
</div>
<p>还有，超广角镜头目前不支持夜景模式也是一个「硬伤」，拍夜间的开阔美景，超广角镜头拍出来的照片有种「脏脏的朦胧感」。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369201" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone26.png" alt="" width="2390" height="1778" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone26.png 2390w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone26-360x268.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone26-768x571.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone26-1024x762.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2390px) 100vw, 2390px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 超广角镜头暂不支持夜间模式，成像「感人」</p>
</div>
<p>看到别人用几十倍变焦拍出来的城市建筑照片，说不羡慕那是骗人的，我非常期待能站在公司的天台上，拍到广州塔尖非常清晰的美景，很可惜 iPhone 11 系列暂时做不到。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369315" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone54.png" alt="" width="1576" height="1178" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone54.png 1576w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone54-360x269.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone54-768x574.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone54-1024x765.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1576px) 100vw, 1576px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ iPhone 11 五倍变焦成片几乎不可放大使用</p>
</div>
<p>各位如果要突突，火力请轻一点，我真的是友军。</p>
<p>只是有点感慨，当年那个突破性提高像素和采用大底 CMOS 的苹果，为什么如今反而成了被别人「突破」的对象。</p>
<h3><strong>宝刀未老，优势仍在</strong></h3>
<p>iPhone 拍照无法满足部分用户的部分需求，并不代表 iPhone 拍照的综合实力不行。</p>
<p>相反，<strong>在不少人心目中，iPhone 仍然是智能手机拍照综合实力 No.1</strong>。</p>
<p>白平衡、饱和度、宽容度这三项，综合来看，和不少安卓旗舰比，iPhone 的表现仍然极其优秀，被支持者冠以「真实」二字。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369203" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_4256.jpg" alt="" width="3024" height="4032" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_4256.jpg 3024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_4256-360x480.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_4256-768x1024.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 3024px) 100vw, 3024px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ iPhone 11 人像模式拍摄，白平衡、饱和度、宽容度都非常优秀，景深和虚化恰当好处，细节也很丰富</p>
</div>
<p>Smart HDR 的优势夸张一点可以用「甩友商两条街」来形容，这个 HDR 是实时的，能在拍摄取景框里就渲染出来，iPhone 拍照「所见即所得」这个认知也要归功于它，背后其实是强大的 A 系列芯片在默默支持。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369317" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone55.gif" alt="" width="448" height="207" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone55.gif 448w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone55-360x166.gif 360w" sizes="(max-width: 448px) 100vw, 448px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 注意看天空在 Smart HDR 加持下的实时渲染效果</p>
</div>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369302" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_9238.jpg" alt="" width="4032" height="3024" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_9238.jpg 4032w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_9238-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_9238-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_9238-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 4032px) 100vw, 4032px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ iPhone 11 拍摄</p>
</div>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369284" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_5280.jpg" alt="" width="1706" height="2275" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_5280.jpg 1706w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_5280-360x480.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_5280-768x1024.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1706px) 100vw, 1706px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ iPhone 11 拍摄，相册 app 编辑</p>
</div>
<p>Deep Fusion 提出了另一种手机拍照的发展思路，<strong>如果可以靠先进的软件算法实现同样甚至更优的清晰效果，算法和高像素硬件到底哪一个才是最优解</strong>？Google 也在朝这个方向努力探索。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369280" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/v2-ab3db897ce55fb406f74d115619b3a25_1440w.jpg" alt="" width="1080" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/v2-ab3db897ce55fb406f74d115619b3a25_1440w.jpg 1080w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/v2-ab3db897ce55fb406f74d115619b3a25_1440w-360x360.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/v2-ab3db897ce55fb406f74d115619b3a25_1440w-768x768.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/v2-ab3db897ce55fb406f74d115619b3a25_1440w-1024x1024.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ iPhone 11 Pro 系列拍摄. 图片来自：Instagram @tldtoday /唐唐 @知乎</p>
</div>
<p>多颗摄像头切换交互体验出色，变焦流畅，成像风格统一。目前在摄像方面能和 iPhone 抗衡的国产旗舰机，在这方面还有很长的路要走，变焦卡顿、成像风格跳跃、操作不便捷等都是硬伤，给拍照体验减分不少。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369304" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone50.gif" alt="" width="672" height="311" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone50.gif 672w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone50-360x167.gif 360w" sizes="(max-width: 672px) 100vw, 672px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 变焦流畅，操作体验也很出色，目前很多国产手机无法做到</p>
</div>
<p>夜景模式用起来十分顺手，系统自动开启，免去手动打开步骤，成像也不会「把黑夜拍成白天」，该暗的地方暗，该亮的地方亮，足以暂时弥补超广角没有夜景模式的缺陷。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369303" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone41.png" alt="" width="1966" height="1426" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone41.png 1966w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone41-360x261.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone41-768x557.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone41-1024x743.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1966px) 100vw, 1966px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ iPhone 11 拍摄，Snapseed 编辑</p>
</div>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369289" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone31.png" alt="" width="1072" height="1428" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone31.png 1072w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone31-360x480.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone31-768x1023.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone31-769x1024.png 769w" sizes="(max-width: 1072px) 100vw, 1072px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ iPhone 11 拍摄，逆光环境下 Smart HDR 表现出色</p>
</div>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369290" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone33.png" alt="" width="1910" height="1422" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone33.png 1910w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone33-360x268.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone33-768x572.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone33-1024x762.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1910px) 100vw, 1910px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ iPhone 11 拍摄，夜景氛围自然</p>
</div>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369305" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone51.png" alt="" width="1530" height="970" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone51.png 1530w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone51-360x228.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone51-768x487.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone51-1024x649.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1530px) 100vw, 1530px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ iPhone 11 拍摄</p>
</div>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369310" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_6784.jpg" alt="" width="5187" height="3894" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_6784.jpg 5187w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_6784-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_6784-768x577.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/IMG_6784-1024x769.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 5187px) 100vw, 5187px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ iPhone 11 拍摄</p>
</div>
<p>总之，要说 iPhone 拍照某些维度掉队了是可以的，但要说它的整体实力掉队了，还言之过早。</p>
<h3><strong>下一代 iPhone 摄影</strong></h3>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369292" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone2-2.jpg" alt="" width="5131" height="3666" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone2-2.jpg 5131w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone2-2-360x257.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone2-2-768x549.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/iPhone2-2-1024x732.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 5131px) 100vw, 5131px" /></p>
<p>下一代 iPhone 即将发布，相信不少人都非常期待它在摄影方面有所突破。</p>
<p>到了现在手机拍照「群雄逐鹿」的时代，如果旗舰 iPhone 继续保持 1200 万像素和 10 倍变焦，不升级超广角镜头像素，不给超广角镜头适配夜间模式，它的拍照优势还能保持多久，真的很难说。</p>
<p>从最开始大家心目中的 No.1，到后来苹果主动把 iPhone 的拍照表述改为「最受用户喜欢/欢迎的摄影系统」，再到现在「iPhone 拍照掉队了」的说法开始流行，反映的是 iPhone 摄影方面的努力已低于用户预期的情况。</p>
<p><strong>作为目前手机行业毫无争议的「老大」苹果，把 iPhone 拍照水平「搞上去」，既是一种必要的商业行为，也是一种引领行业的担当和勇气。</strong></p>
<p><strong>期待有一天 iPhone 有底气再说一次：This changes everything, again!</strong></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><em>封面图来源：丁亦然（<a href="https://unsplash.com/@yiranding">Unsplash</a>）</em></p>
